dataObjects.description: Endemic to Lake Malawi where it has been recorded at Boadzulu Island, Chinyamwezi Island, Chinyankhwazi Island and Makokola reef.

dataObjects.subject: http://rs.tdwg.org/ontology/voc/SPMInfoItems#Distribution
dataObjects.description: Africa:  endemic to Lake Malawi.  Occurs in Boadzulu and Chinyankwazi Islands.  Also recorded from Chinyamwezi Island (Ref. 26709).

dataObjects.subject: http://rs.tdwg.org/ontology/voc/SPMInfoItems#Morphology
dataObjects.description: Dorsal spines (total): 16 - 18; Dorsal soft rays (total): 8 - 9; Analsoft rays: 6 - 8

dataObjects.subject: http://rs.tdwg.org/ontology/voc/SPMInfoItems#DiagnosticDescription
dataObjects.description: Gill rakers on first ceratobranchial 7-9; gill rakers on first epibranchial 1-3.
